data.description: Opportunity is knocking for the lucky buyer of this amazing property with great potential! This rare 4 bedroom home has a great, spacious open concept design perfect for a large family or for entertaining. Spacious and well designed kitchen has wood cabinets and granite countertops, brand new stainless steel appliances. Updated bathrooms. 2021 A/C. Beautiful marble floors in common areas and laminate in bedrooms. This amazing home has 2 master suites, one of them perfect for in laws suite and many more possibilities. Fenced backyard and expanded driveway. Great location with great schools, easy access to major highways, restaurants, hospitals, beach, airport and shopping! Community is gated with beautiful lakes and pathways.
